thread.title_full: Thread Logic reviewed by Kelly Cunningham

author: Kelly Cunningham
title: Kelly Cunningham
text: I had a vector that they were able to accurately digitize to better results than I was even expecting. They are very professional and great communicators. They sent images of stitched samples before they billed and committed the order. Very happy customer!
